IN ORDER TO USE THE APPLICATION YOU SHOULD FOLLOW THE STEPS:

1. Install the mail application from the UNIX enviroment using the comand: sudo apt-get install mailnag 
or use sudo yum-install mailnag for the Red Hat Enterprise.

2. After the instalation of the mail application copy the script in a non-volatile folder like: /mnt /opt /etc
and make it bootable in the fstab configuration of linux.

3. Run the script using the command: while true; do /mnt/Email-notification-Backup.txt; done &

4. Include the command in the init or init.d tab to make it bootable at the start of the OS.
